Open `.claude/skills/add-section/SKILL.md` and follow it exactly. It is plain
markdown written for any agent. In short: load PLAYBOOK.md §1 to §3 plus the
matching recipe (R1 homepage section, R2 subpage, R5 nav, R6 new style), write
the five-line spec first (job, voice, mobile layout, desktop layout, ground
colour), build from the blessed components with CSS appended to app/globals.css,
then run the finishing gate and verify at 375 and 1280 widths.
